{"tid":1113845,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國嚴控選出兩教廷認可主教","createTime":"2019-04-18T07:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T07:36:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e0e3145093bed9426992982bd5212c089acfb7","tid":1113845,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190418/20658649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190418%2F20658649&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSFRUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=60139e0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190418%2F20658649&h=2daee17c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190418/20658649</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國嚴控選出兩教廷認可主教<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190418/large/a1704a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190418%2Flarge%2Fa1704a.gif&h=616a51dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國與梵蒂岡去年9月簽訂不對外公開《主教任命臨時協議》後，中國近日正式「選出」教廷認可的兩名主教。兩場選舉過程均受當局嚴格控制，且兩個教區均只有一名候選人。外媒引述不具名的教廷消息人士指，形容這場「選舉」僅是「走程序、搞形勢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190418/large/a1704b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190418%2Flarge%2Fa1704b.gif&h=efe5563f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北京世界園藝博覽會正在調試夜景燈光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當局推薦23信徒投票<br />\n<br />\n《亞洲新聞網》報道，54歲前副主教姚順於本月9日，被選為內蒙古集寧教區主敎；兩日後，曾在加拿大服務的胥紅偉神父被選為山西漢中教區主教。兩場主教「選舉」均由數十名神父修女，以及由當局推薦的23名信徒投票。兩場投票都分別在當地飯店內舉行，過程均受當局嚴格控制，並在政府官員、中國天主教組織以及警察百多人在場「見證」下進行，且兩個教區亦只有一名候選人。教廷消息人士透露，形容這場「選舉」僅是「走程序、搞形勢」，而選出的主教其後需由當局再次確認，「這簡直是笑話」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，儘管大陸近期頻頻打壓天主教地下教會，上演選舉鬧劇，卻無礙中梵關係升溫。梵蒂岡昨更宣佈，本月29日底將應中國之邀，參加北京世界園藝博覽會，並開設展館。對於這種互動，教廷文化部長拉瓦西樞機主教（Gianfranco Ravasi）對此表示，此行目的是「創造對話的氣氛」。<br />\n<br />\n《亞洲新聞網》/ 路透社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n監管升級 良心軍醫蔣彥永「被住院」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n購平治漏油 女碩士維權獲換車"},{"pid":"40ff837a1c4e040ebc0d4fce5cd857ddd789ccc5","tid":1113845,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWn6T0g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWn6T0g.png&h=dc9c6578&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96e2fb8aa6d8f4fc1bfcd68a03ca2cb9c3d56093","tid":1113845,"uid":61271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"呢個教宗一定落地獄"},{"pid":"16f49addb2445bc4fba0f6bcbb5c1bc250736135","tid":1113845,"uid":76216,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:17:50.000Z","msg":"所以點解聖母院會比火燒  唔係冇原因"},{"pid":"25b459fe2c0e049375b0bba9614137013a412550","tid":1113845,"uid":54502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"偽教宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02680318e4a77c9f8a32f11a6db99feea1799416","tid":1113845,"uid":36481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:27:05.000Z","msg":"睇清楚你地個教宗啊<br />\n天主教徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ef5e12f1c8f4a724e6d233157583e072d90f3d","tid":1113845,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"習總大定天主大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}